  "text": "It follows that e β 1 is a ratio of partial AUC odds for X + 1 to X. When e β 1 > 1, the partial AUC odds are an increasing function of X, and accuracy increases with X. If e β 1 < 1, the partial AUC odds are a decreasing function of X. Refer to [CITATION_1] for details about model specification.",
